metadata.name: Void Creature
metadata.description:
Picture of an strange mutated humanoid floating in uncomfortable space.
The creature is wrapped around a constantly overgrown mass, which it is forced to burn by releasing the energy of its body. 
This is his way of moving through outer space. 

3000x4395 pixels, 300DPI

Additionally, the —Åustomer will receive about 10 GB of psd sources and materials of the work in progress.
I worked on this one really hard and long. 
Work has passed thru many iterations so maybe you will interested in seeing all of them, from first to last.
You can use all of them as you wish.
